WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to Sadhana — calm guided yoga.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Mountain Pose — find your foundation.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Tree Pose — balance with soft focus.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Downward Dog — lengthen through the spine.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Low Lunge — open hips and breathe.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Child's Pose — rest and reset.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Legs Up the Wall — restore gently.
